(77, NULL, 'Old Cuban', '{\"recipe\": [{\"Method\": \"Pour all ingredients into cocktail shaker except the wine, shake well with ice, strain into chilled elegant cocktail glass. Top up with the sparkling wine.\", \"Garnish\": \"Garnish with mint springs.\", \"Ingredients\": {\"Aged Rum\": \"45 ml\", \"Mint Leaves\": \"6 Pieces\", \"Simple Syrup\": \"30 ml\", \"Fresh Lime Juice\": \"22.5 ml\", \"Angostura Bitters\": \"2 Dashes\", \"Brut Champagne or Prosecco\": \"60 ml\"}}]}', 'Old-Cuban.jpg', 'New Era Drinks'),
